WEBVTT

00:00:03.796 --> 00:00:06.007
<i>Is the destiny of mankind controlled</i>

00:00:06.007 --> 00:00:08.050
<i>by some transcendental</i>

00:00:08.259 --> 00:00:10.261
<i>entity or law?</i>

00:00:10.428 --> 00:00:12.680
<i>Is it like the hand of God</i>

00:00:12.763 --> 00:00:16.767
<i>hovering above?</i>

00:00:18.602 --> 00:00:20.980
<i>At least it is true...</i>

00:00:21.022 --> 00:00:23.399
<i>that man has no control</i>

00:00:23.399 --> 00:00:27.778
<i>even over his own will.</i>

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:35.074
